<Content>Beuttiful place--Bad Food After a 2 hour ride from San Juan we found the place. We wanted to find the Bar but they don't have one. We sat in the resturant which is very nice and ordered drinks. It was very dark we could not see how lovely this place was. The rooms are one step up from camping out Very old and dirty. When we woke up in the morning I thought I was in paradice.You are so close to the water,the beach and pool are great. Not only is the food at the motel bad but it is also terrible at all the local resturants.This is not a tourist area and you don't feel welcomed. 
